# Private resume variants — YOUR personalized .tex live here and must NEVER be
# committed (they hold personal data). The whole directories are gitignored.
# `python -m job_seeker init` scaffolds them locally from resume_template/.
LaTeX_Resume_CN/
LaTeX_Resume_EN/

# Outputs (only track the README)
outputs/*
!outputs/README.md

